{
  "id": "2666957454_2",
  "title": "微信重大更新！网友：聊天记录终于有救了！",
  "content": "<div class=\"rich_media_content js_underline_content defaultNoSetting\" id=\"js_content\">\n <p>\n  <span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">\n   日前，微信派发布消息，微信迎来了重大更新——优化聊天记录备份。\n  </span>\n </p>\n <p>\n  <span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">\n   <br/>\n  </span>\n </p>\n <p>\n  <span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">\n   <span style=\"font-size: 18px;color: rgb(0, 122, 170);\">\n    <strong>\n     “外援”进场\n    </strong>\n   </span>\n   <span style=\"color: rgb(171, 25, 66);\">\n   </span>\n  </span>\n </p>\n <p>\n  <span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">\n   <br/>\n  </span>\n </p>\n <p>\n  <span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">\n   现在，手机微信能将聊天记录备份到 U 盘、移动硬盘等外部存储设备。当家庭用户共用一个硬盘或电脑进行聊天记录备份，也不会互相干扰、泄露隐私。\n  </span>\n </p>\n <p>\n  <span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">\n   <br/>\n  </span>\n </p>\n <p>\n  <span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">\n   点击“微信-我-设置-通用-聊天记录迁移与备份-备份与恢复”。\n  </span>\n </p>\n <p>\n  <span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">\n   <br/>\n  </span>\n </p>\n <p>\n  <img alt=\"图片\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-backh=\"1191\" data-backw=\"578\" data-imgfileid=\"519473795\" data-ratio=\"2.061111111111111\" data-w=\"1080\" src=\"/static/res/logo/https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/sz_mmbiz_jpg/OiaFLUqewuIBreRvRmnQTp2O9Un5BcX7vnX5awyPF1iaiahXBvqex6OatRliaqOamVGPOiaujviaJzkEBjo0VvSDAfsg/640?wx_fmt=jpeg&amp;from=appmsg&amp;wxfrom=5&amp;wx_lazy=1&amp;tp=wxpic\" style=\"outline: 0px;width: 1080px !important;visibility: visible !important;\"/>\n </p>\n <p>\n  <span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">\n   <br/>\n  </span>\n </p>\n <p>\n  <span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">\n   <span style=\"font-size: 18px;color: rgb(0, 122, 170);\">\n    <strong>\n     自动备份\n    </strong>\n   </span>\n   <span style=\"color: rgb(171, 25, 66);\">\n   </span>\n  </span>\n </p>\n <p>\n  <span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">\n   <br/>\n  </span>\n </p>\n <p>\n  <span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">\n   手动档切自动挡，很省心。\n  </span>\n </p>\n <p>\n  <span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">\n   <br/>\n  </span>\n </p>\n <p>\n  <span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">\n   当系统识别到手机已连接到开启“自动备份”时选择的电脑/外部设备时，将会进行自动备份。\n  </span>\n </p>\n <p>\n  <span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">\n   <br/>\n  </span>\n </p>\n <p>\n  <img alt=\"图片\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-backh=\"1192\" data-backw=\"578\" data-imgfileid=\"519473797\" data-ratio=\"2.062037037037037\" data-w=\"1080\" src=\"/static/res/logo/https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/sz_mmbiz_jpg/OiaFLUqewuIByQSia9sFRyFqaPe60IgxREic8w85qMD2BfBQJ5BLnkgtM5T1NCibt7yWia1ViciaFSqPCo9fwcXlaMgzw/640?wx_fmt=jpeg&amp;from=appmsg&amp;wxfrom=5&amp;wx_lazy=1&amp;tp=wxpic\" style=\"outline: 0px;width: 577.995px !important;visibility: visible !important;\"/>\n </p>\n <p>\n  <span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">\n   <br/>\n  </span>\n </p>\n <p>\n  <span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">\n  </span>\n  <span style=\"font-size: 18px;color: rgb(0, 122, 170);\">\n   <strong>\n    灵活备份\n   </strong>\n  </span>\n </p>\n <p>\n  <span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">\n   <br/>\n  </span>\n </p>\n <p>\n  <span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">\n   备份范围、备份时间，随你心意。\n  </span>\n </p>\n <p>\n  <span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">\n   <br/>\n  </span>\n </p>\n <p>\n  <span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">\n   可灵活按需选择备份“全部聊天”“除了折叠的群的全部聊天”，也可根据标签或手动选择指定聊天进行备份；还可根据指定时间进行备份。\n  </span>\n </p>\n <p>\n  <span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">\n   <br/>\n  </span>\n </p>\n <p>\n  <img alt=\"图片\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-backh=\"1192\" data-backw=\"578\" data-imgfileid=\"519473796\" data-ratio=\"2.062037037037037\" data-w=\"1080\" src=\"/static/res/logo/https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/sz_mmbiz_jpg/OiaFLUqewuIByQSia9sFRyFqaPe60IgxRELrjupPPtY6BcPSo1mdXwWibicZcc0lElWZj4C3FlhVicompkLzS1fcmFQ/640?wx_fmt=jpeg&amp;from=appmsg&amp;wxfrom=5&amp;wx_lazy=1&amp;tp=wxpic\" style=\"outline: 0px;width: 1080px !important;visibility: visible !important;\"/>\n </p>\n <p>\n  <span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">\n   <br/>\n  </span>\n </p>\n <p>\n  <span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">\n   <span style=\"color: rgb(171, 25, 66);\">\n    <strong>\n    </strong>\n   </span>\n  </span>\n  <span style=\"font-size: 18px;color: rgb(0, 122, 170);\">\n   <strong>\n    聊天记录迁移\n   </strong>\n  </span>\n </p>\n <p>\n  <span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">\n   <br/>\n  </span>\n </p>\n <p>\n  <span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">\n   除此之外，用户更换新机后无需在旧手机登录微信，\n   <strong>\n    新手机扫扫码就能一键导出聊天记录到新机。\n   </strong>\n   支持直接从另一台手机或其他设备导入，也可导出到电脑、另一台手机或平板。\n  </span>\n </p>\n <p>\n  <span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">\n   <br/>\n  </span>\n </p>\n <p>\n  <span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">\n   *点击“微信-我-设置-通用-聊天记录管理-导入与导出”。\n  </span>\n </p>\n <p>\n  <span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">\n   <br/>\n  </span>\n </p>\n <p>\n  <img alt=\"图片\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-backh=\"1192\" data-backw=\"578\" data-imgfileid=\"519473799\" data-ratio=\"2.062037037037037\" data-w=\"1080\" src=\"/static/res/logo/https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/sz_mmbiz_jpg/OiaFLUqewuIBreRvRmnQTp2O9Un5BcX7v5icFQNu64tXwHPetln5bgDulRZGtKw9YafTC4H2ByJgFweckvl9jLKA/640?wx_fmt=jpeg&amp;from=appmsg&amp;wxfrom=5&amp;wx_lazy=1&amp;tp=wxpic\" style=\"outline: 0px;width: 1080px !important;visibility: visible !important;\"/>\n </p>\n <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\">\n  <br/>\n </p>\n <section mp-original-font-size=\"16\" mp-original-line-height=\"28\" style=\"text-align: center;\">\n  <span style=\"font-size: 18px;color: rgb(0, 122, 170);\">\n   <strong>\n    你还期待微信上线哪些新功能？\n   </strong>\n  </span>\n </section>\n <p mp-original-font-size=\"16\" mp-original-line-height=\"28\" style=\"text-align: center;\">\n  <span style=\"font-size: 18px;color: rgb(0, 122, 170);\">\n   <strong>\n    评论区等你！\n   </strong>\n  </span>\n </p>\n <p mp-original-font-size=\"16\" mp-original-line-height=\"28\">\n  <br/>\n </p>\n <hr style='max-width: 100%;letter-spacing: 0.544px;white-space: normal;font-family: -apple-system-font, system-ui, \"Helvetica Neue\", \"PingFang SC\", \"Hiragino Sans GB\", \"Microsoft YaHei UI\", \"Microsoft YaHei\", Arial, sans-serif;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);border-style: solid;border-right-width: 0px;border-bottom-width: 0px;